OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fwith variable amounts of cloud,
OL,9,Fperhaps the odd spot of rain later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FDry with with some bright or
OL,12,Fsunny spells although some cloud
OL,13,Faround at times. Warm.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry with
OL,16,Fbright spells on Friday, best of the
OL,17,Fsunshine in the east. Rain spreading
OL,18,Fsoutheast on Saturday, drier with a
OL,19,Ffew showers later. Mainly dry on
OL,20,FSunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
